IMMEDIATE
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA(BHARAT 'SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT(MANTRIMANDAL SACHI VALAYA)
Department of Cabinet Affairs (Mantrimandal Karya Vibhag)
New Delhi, 7 June, 1973.
17 Jyaistha, 1895.
The undersigned is directed to state that with
effect from June 6, 1973, the President has been pleased
to direct that Shrimati Indira Gandhi, prime Minister
(pradhan Mantri) shall also be Minister of Steel and
Mines (Ispat aur Khan Mantri).
(G.P. Chadha)

All Members of the Council of Ministers.
